<h2 id="variable-board-size">Variable Board Size</h2>

<p>When starting a game, a user should be able to indicate the height and width of the board. All of your validations should still work with these variable board dimensions</p>

<h2 id="custom-ships">Custom Ships</h2>

<p>When starting a game, a user can optionally create the ships they will play with. They should be able to give each ship a name and length, and be able to create as many of these ships as they want.</p>

<h2 id="intelligent-computer">Intelligent Computer</h2>

<p>The computer should make an educated guess of what coordinate to fire on.</p>
